Teltoli winces as the two darts hit her, and she puts a hand to her, 
her vision swimming. She groaned quietly, and her wings failed her, 
sending her in a direct plummet for the ground.

'I'm sorry Windlord and Aerotaur..' 

The hit would have knocked the air out of her lungs, except she was 
already out cold by the time she landed on her back, eyes closed. The 
shot from Fenox whizzed by her, missed because of her falling.


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Starlight/Fenox::
> 
> Starling brings up a hand to block the rapier, yelling in pain as 
it 
> digs into her circuits. He drops her missile launcher, firing two 
> more darts at Teltoli. She had seen her other two darts hit the 
> Maximal. The tranquilizer didn't act instantly, but two darts 
should 
> be enough to take out a bot twice Teltoli's size.
> 
> Starlight flies back, pulling out Teltoli's rapier out of her arm. 
> Overhead, Fenox flies by, firing down at Teltoli's head with her 
> automatic rifle.
